title: Bug 109350 - Output parameter missing in data set dialog
description: The output parameter does not display in the data set dialog when calling a stored procedure from Oracle database.
OB: The output parameter value does not appear in the data set dialog for the stored procedure query result.
EB: The output parameter value should be visible in the data set dialog for the stored procedure query result.
SR:
To reproduce:
1. Call the stored procedure from Oracle database.
2. Check the data set dialog.
3. Observe that the output parameter value is missing.
